trans_title: 不能说的女儿 第二季
introduction: After reconnecting with her mothers side of the family, Billie Carter (Jessica Mauboy) returns to the city finally knowing that she is Jack Nortons secret daughter. Which means shes now a millionaire. Billie throws herself into her glamorous new life, and just by being Billie, she changes everyone elses world for the better. But theres one thing missing. For all the fairy dust Billie leaves in her wake, she keeps her own heart firmly guarded against falling in love. Surely there must be someone out there for her? But as her career takes off, tragedy threatens. Will Billie realise her dreams, only to lose whats most important to her?
chinese_title: 不能说的女儿 第二季
